      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At least two independent test conditions (e.g., load rate or construct offset) to bound model applicability.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717 standard offset (35 mm) and single crosshead rate (25 mm/min) across both laboratories. A second offset or load rate was not included in the test plan. This factor is below the required level; the shortfall is acknowledged and noted as a limitation of the current validation scope."
    },
    {
