      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions, load) demonstrably equivalent to test conditions within quantified tolerances.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions mirror ASTM F1717 fixture: superior block fixed, inferior block loaded at 35 mm offset, frictionless platen interfaces. Fixture compliance measured experimentally (0.12 mm/kN) and incorporated as a spring element in the model. Material inputs matched to coupon test results from the same production lot as test samples. Equivalency confirmed at Gradation 3."
    },
